question: How many leads were closed successfully (won) vs lost?
sql: SELECT CASE WHEN probability = 100 THEN 'Won' WHEN probability = 0 THEN 'Lost' ELSE 'In Progress' END AS lead_status, COUNT(*) AS lead_count FROM crm_lead GROUP BY lead_status;
models_answer:
SELECT CASE WHEN s.is_won THEN 'Won' ELSE 'Lost' END AS lead_status, COUNT(l.id) AS lead_count
FROM crm_lead l
INNER JOIN crm_stage s ON l.stage_id = s.id
WHERE l.date_closed IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY lead_status;
